<h1 id="v.-interpretation">V. Interpretation</h1>
<h2 id="a.-framework-validation">A. Framework Validation</h2>
<p>Our testing framework revealed precise relationships between test
objectives and measured results, validating consciousness as a quantum
field phenomenon. Let us examine how each level contributed to this
